From the Infowars web site ::

On the Monday, April 23, 2012 edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with Dr. Corey Gold, host of the Noon Balloon show on KSCO talk radio. He is a former practicing dentist who made the transition into the business world and founded several businesses. Mr. Gold is a nationally recognized speaker and a trainer in the entrepreneurial world of network marketing. 

Alex also covers the European Space Agency decision to loft a new surveillance satellite that will measure man-made carbon emissions from space in order to "hunt down" violators of international climate agreements, allowing Big Brother to enforce a future tax on CO2 emissions.
